name: Peace And Happiness
alt: Naomi standing and making peace signs with her hands.
description: She hopes you have a great day!

name: Blissful Rest
alt: Naomi laying on her stomach with her legs bent upwards.
description: Naomi can't sit still. She's always changing poses and kicking her legs around.

name: Kick Back and Relax
alt: Naomi leaning back with her legs in the air.
description: It's nice to stretch out and relax.

name: Chibi
alt: Chibi style art of Naomi
description: Everyone needs a chibi art, right??

name: Sitting Down
alt: Naomi sitting on her knees with her hands in her lap
description: Want to sit next to her?

name: Playful
alt: Naomi kneeling, facing away from you, looking over her shoulder with her tongue stuck out
description: Sometimes she likes to play around.

name: Chance to Breathe
alt: Naomi sitting with her legs folded over each other
description: A nice relaxing moment to sit down.

name: Feeling Cute
alt: Naomi sitting with one leg stretched out and the other crossed over
description: There are definitely days where Naomi feels cuter than normal.

name: Time to Get Serious
alt: Sketch of Naomi from the waist up
description: Naomi focuses hard when she's working.

name: Colourless
alt: Colourless sketch of Naomi from the waist up
description: Someone was kind enough to gift Naomi this quick sketch.

name: Stretchy Time!
alt: Naomi sitting with her arms around her legs, one leg extended
description: Always important to keep yourself flexible and limber.

name: Slightly Shy
alt: Naomi sitting and giving a shy look
description: She can be shy sometimes, especially when someone is being affectionate toward her.

name: Laying Down
alt: Naomi lying on her bed
description: She might even sneak in a nap...

name: Exhausted
alt: Naomi sitting on her knees, looking up at you with a tired expression
description: Sometimes Naomi struggles to keep going, after pushing too hard.

name: Bedtime
alt: Naomi laying in bed
description: Time to unwind before she passes out.

name: Playful Moments
alt: Naomi crouching down with her tongue stuck out.
description: Playtime is her favourite time.

name: Nice and Cosy
alt: Naomi sitting, hugging her legs
description: It can feel good to take a moment to hug yourself.

name: A Moment's Respite
alt: Naomi sitting with her legs extended
description: She always takes advantage of a chance to sit and relax.

name: Who Wants a Hug?
alt: Naomi extending her arms as if offering a hug
description: She loves giving hugs. Hopefully you love receiving them!

name: Shrine Maiden
alt: Naomi in her shrine maiden outfit, surrounded by a magical aura and sakura petals.
description: She's always wanted to become a shrine maiden...

name: Casual Outing
alt: Naomi in her casual dress, her hair frizzy.
description: Sometimes she doesn't feel like doing her hair.

name: A Li'l Flirty
alt: Naomi sitting with her hands clasped and her legs stretched out toward you.
description: Naomi was feeling playfully flirty.

name: The True Queen
alt: Naomi wearing her monarch dress, standing with her hand over her chest.
description: She may not be royalty, but she feels like royalty.

name: Pixel Naomi
alt: Pixel art of Naomi
description: She's ready to star in a retro video game.

name: Drinky Drink
alt: Naomi wearing her galaxy dress, sitting on the edge of the bed with a glass of wine in her hand.
description: A glass of wine before bed helps her turn off her thoughts and sleep.

name: Secret Witch
alt: Naomi dressed as a witch, riding her broom.
description: She is actually Wiccan, so it fits?

name: Padoru
alt: Padoru Naomi! Wearing a santa outfit and carrying a bag of gifts.
description: HASHIRE SORI YO!

name: Vampire
alt: Naomi in a black evening dress, laying across a coffin.
description: She's been called a vampire before, with how little she sleeps...

name: Sun's Caress
alt: Naomi laying in a field of flowers, wearing a red sundress.
description: Naomi rarely gets outside, so when she does she takes the time to enjoy it.

name: Hard at Work
alt: Cat girl Naomi, hard at work on her laptop.
description: She rarely stops working...

name: Pet the Floof
alt: Cat girl Naomi, holding her fluffy tail.
description: Always pet the floof.

name: Sketch
alt: Naomi in her daily outfit.
description: Naomi's typical attire - someone sketched this from a photo of her.

name: A Supportive Partner
alt: Naomi working while Cora bites her face.
description: She's getting support from Cora in her own way.

name: Cutie Convention
alt: The sexy ladies club, featuring Naomi, Lillith, Cora, Nashi, and Seri.
description: Naomi with a bunch of her cute friends!

name: Vacation Plans
alt: Naomi having a relaxing day at the beach
description: Spending a day at the beach is her favourite choice to get away from work.

name: The Great Mother of Mothers
alt: Bust portrait of Naomi, wearing black lipstick and pink blush, her hair down.
description: Even when she is still getting ready for the day, she is always available to comfort you.

name: Snug as a Bug
alt: Emote of Naomi sitting on the ground wrapped in a purple blanket.
description: She loves to be cosy and warm.

name: Pondering
alt: Naomi sitting on a half-wall, lost in thought.
description: She has once again become lost in her thoughts.

name: Furry Friends
alt: Naomi hiding under the couch with a friend as four other furry friends run rampant through the room.
description: When you're outnumbered, hiding is the best option.

name: Naomi Dango
alt: Naomi being picked up with chopsticks like a dumpling.
description: The tastiest of all snacks.
